OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fslowly fading away with skies largely
OL,7,Fclearing during the second half of the
OL,8,Fnight. Some gusty winds are likely at
OL,9,Ftimes overnight, particularly over
OL,10,Fhills and near the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FVariable amounts of cloud but
OL,13,Fa dry and mainly bright day for many.
OL,14,FGentle or moderate breezes continue
OL,15,Fthrough the day, but feeling
OL,16,Fpleasantly warm, particularly in any
OL,17,Fsheltered spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
